name: A Second to Midnight
description:
The sound of the train as I wait in vain
The screeching of the rails and the notifications of my e-mail
My thoughts flying as the nature is spying
It is always Second to Midnight
-ÜTSY

A genesis artwork for the Wood-HEN Crafts by The Collective

3D Artwork and Animation by LILITH
Enhancements and Sounds by ÜTSY
